<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Wed, 06 Sep 2023 19:46:25 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Google Workspace's file lock stops colleagues messing with your documents]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Google <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/pro-tips-for-using-google-drive-150029273.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/pro-tips-for-using-google-drive-150029273.html">Workspace 用户</a>将获得一项新功能，以防止同事弄乱他们的文档。用户现在可以锁定他们的 Google Drive 文件，这有助于减少与多个团队成员共享时不必要的评论和更改。虽然这不是最具革命性的功能，但它肯定会派上用场 - 特别是对于<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-workspace-storage-increase-140949440.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/google-workspace-storage-increase-140949440.html">使用和共享大量公开</a>可见文档的公司而言。</p><p>锁定文档会将其置于只读模式，这意味着查看者无法对其进行编辑、评论或留下建议。该文档将保持只读模式，直到被其所有者解锁。谷歌在一篇<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/09/lock-files-more-easily-in-google-drive.html" data-original-link="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/09/lock-files-more-easily-in-google-drive.html">博客文章</a>中表示，这项新功能将“简化云端硬盘中限制文件的过程”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>以前，您可以在共享文档或文件时或通过 Google Drive API 调用来锁定文档或文件。新的锁定功能简化了操作：右键单击要锁定的文件，从弹出菜单中滚动到文件信息，然后选择锁定。</p><p>文件锁定功能已在某些快速发布域中推出，并将在接下来的 15 天内继续推出。计划发布域中的用户预计将于 9 月 20 日开始看到该功能，推出期也有类似的 15 天。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/google-workspaces-file-lock-stops-colleagues-messing-with-your-documents-194625235.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-workspaces-file-lock-stops-colleagues-messing-with-your-documents-194625235.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 215b24c5-8988-4148-be84-9cd74d126e41</guid><dc:creator>斯蒂芬妮·巴恩斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 19:46:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694030125</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T19:55:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Stephanie Barnes]]></category><media:content height="1517" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/23e1f650-4cef-11ee-afef-5530533c376c" width="2497"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1517" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/23e1f650-4cef-11ee-afef-5530533c376c" width="2497"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Google]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Google Workspace word logo surrounded by a cloud of Google app icons.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Google Workspace]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Roku lays off 300 workers and removes streaming content to save money]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Roku 似乎正在认真收紧资金。 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/roku-layoffs-content-impairment-charge-cost-cutting-1235714653/">据<em>Variety 报道，该公司除了采取一系列其他成本削减措施外，还解雇了 300 多名员工，占员工总数的 10%。</em></a>这些裁员只是一个开始，Roku 还删除了流媒体内容、整合了办公空间并减少了外部服务费用。这里的目标是大幅降低运营费用同比增长率。</p><p>该公司尚未宣布将从其各个流媒体平台中删除哪些内容，以及这些内容是否会从第三方提供商或内部项目（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/weird-the-weird-al-yankovic-story-roku-channel-150004709.html">最近发布的怪异阿尔传记片）中剔除。</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net/CIK-0001428439/86418ee8-626b-49f2-95fc-c425688d9837.pdf">根据美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 的一份文件，Roku 对这些削减非常重视，以至于愿意在删除这些内容后支付 6500 万美元的减值费用。</a>此外，该公司还计划拨款超过 4500 万至 6500 万美元，为离职员工提供遣散费，并为放弃办公空间提供高达 2 亿美元的资金。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.barrons.com/articles/layoffs-alphabet-meta-microsoft-stock-performance-8c5638bd">与往常一样，</a>股市对裁员和相关紧缩措施表示欢迎，消息传出后，Roku 的股价上涨了 9%，随后又稳定在 4% 左右，涨幅较为温和。截至本文撰写时，股价仍在波动。</p><p>这是 Roku 不到一年内的第三轮裁员。早在 11 月， <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/roku-layoffs-streaming-2022-201541882.html">该公司就解雇了 200 名员工，</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/roku-will-lay-off-another-200-workers-132908304.html">今年 3 月又裁掉了 200 名员工。</a>解雇通知书总数为 700 份，约占员工总数的 25%。正如预期的那样，该公司还宣布暂时推迟招聘新员工。</p><p>经过这一轮重组和相关减值支出后，Roku 希望第三季度净收入增加至 835 美元至 8.75 亿美元，调整后的息税折旧摊销前利润 (EBITDA) 从负 40 美元升至负 2000 万美元。百万。然而，就连 Roku 也承认这些数字存在不确定性，并在第二季度致股东的信中指出，鉴于 WGA 和 SAG-AFTRA 正在进行的罢工，“宏观环境继续造成不确定性”。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/roku-lays-off-300-workers-and-removes-streaming-content-to-save-money-183715207.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/roku-lays-off-300-workers-and-removes-streaming-content-to-save-money-183715207.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 90a0e3e7-ae56-467f-83c0-55dac87bb400</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 18:37:15 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694027538</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T19:12:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1429" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2a1e3de0-4ce9-11ee-bcf6-fba721777a33" width="2175"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1429" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/2a1e3de0-4ce9-11ee-bcf6-fba721777a33" width="2175"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Wikimedia Commons]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A still image of an old Roku XD | S set-top box.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Roku XD | S]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Grammys will consider that viral song with Drake and The Weeknd AI vocals for awards after all]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今年早些时候，一首<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/generative-ai/"><ins>由人工智能生成的</ins></a>歌曲在网上疯传，其背后的人已将这首歌曲提交给格莱美奖考虑。唱片学院已声明此类作品<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ai-generated-music-wont-win-a-grammy-anytime-soon-211855194.html"><ins>不符合某些锣的资格</ins></a>。然而，据<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://variety.com/2023/music/news/ai-generated-drake-the-weeknd-song-submitted-for-grammys-1235714805/"><em><ins>Variety 报道</ins></em></a>，《Heart on My Sleeve》背后的化名者 Ghostwriter 已将这首歌曲列入年度最佳说唱歌曲和年度歌曲类别。这两项都是歌曲创作方面的荣誉。该学院表示，它对大部分由人类创作的奖励曲目持开放态度，即使实际录音主要是人工智能生成的。</p><p>代笔人创作了这首歌的歌词，而不是让<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/chatgpt/"><ins>ChatGPT 等</ins></a>人来做。但他们并没有演唱或说唱这些歌词，而是采用了生成式人工智能模型来模仿 Drake 和 The Weeknd 的声音，这帮助这首歌引起了轰动。艺术家旗下的唱片公司环球音乐集团对此并不满意，并<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/copyright-in-spotlight-after-streaming-platforms-pull-ai-generated-drake-song-183513972.html"><ins>提出版权主张，要求</ins></a>将《Heart on My Sleeve》从流媒体服务中删除。不过在此之前，这首歌在 Spotify 上的收听量已达数十万，在 TikTok 上的收听量也超过 1500 万。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/05/arts/music/ghostwriter-whiplash-travis-scott-21-savage.html"><em><ins>《纽约时报》</ins></em></a>报道，在过去的几个月里，Ghostwriter 和他们的团队一直在向学院高层等行业大佬示好。事实证明，代笔作家实际上可能有机会获得格莱美奖。 “就创意而言，它绝对合格，因为它是由人类编写的，”学院首席执行官小哈维·梅森 (Harvey Mason Jr.) 告诉《<em>泰晤士报》</em> 。</p><p>不过，从目前的情况来看，似乎存在一个主要障碍。对于一首有资格获得格莱美奖的歌曲来说，它需要通过实体店、在线零售商和流媒体服务等在美国进行“广泛发行”。据报道，Ghostwriter 已经意识到了这一限制，但尚不清楚他们计划如何解决这个问题。</p><p>无论如何，这很可能是奖励在艺术中使用生成式人工智能的煤矿里的金丝雀。许多创意人士都关心这个问题。一些人指责生成人工智能系统的运营商<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sarah-silverman-sues-openai-and-meta-over-copyright-infringement-175322447.html"><ins>使用受版权保护的作品</ins></a>来训练他们的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/getty-images-sues-the-maker-of-ai-art-generator-stable-diffusion-over-data-scraping-allegations-184502897.html"><ins>语言学习模型</ins></a>，而正在进行的演员罢工的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/striking-actors-say-rejected-ai-proposal-would-let-studios-use-their-likeness-without-fair-pay-000025878.html">一个主要症结</a>是表演者是否会因为使用他们的数字肖像而得到公平的补偿。生成式人工智能模型的输出是否可以被视为真正的原创作品也是一个有争议的话题。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-grammys-will-consider-that-viral-song-with-drake-and-the-weeknd-ai-vocals-for-awards-after -all-181211888.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-grammys-will-consider-that-viral-song-with-drake-and-the-weeknd-ai-vocals-for-awards-after-all-181211888.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 69e71e9f-ee61-4088-9560-e145c8c36741</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 18:12:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694023933</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T18:12:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2212" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2019-02/b0823b40-2a3c-11e9-9df7-6e3cae3cfafb" width="3500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2212" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-images/2019-02/b0823b40-2a3c-11e9-9df7-6e3cae3cfafb" width="3500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Carlo Allegri / Reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[60th Annual Grammy Awards – Show – New York, U.S., 28/01/2018 – Grammy Awards trophies are displayed backstage during the pre-telecast. REUTERS/Carlo Allegri]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[AWARDS-GRAMMY/]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best fitness trackers for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>健身追踪器并没有消亡，如果您正在阅读本文，您可能是让这些小设备保持活力的人之一。像 Apple Watch 和三星 Galaxy Watch 这样的智能手表几乎已经占据了主流可穿戴设备领域，但对于那些希望小工具始终做好一件事的人来说，不起眼的健身追踪器仍然是一个选择：准确跟踪健身和健康指标，无需您从其他可穿戴设备收到的大量通知。尽管存在阻力，仍然有很多健身手环和 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gps-running-watch-141513957.html">手表</a>可供选择。 Engadget 对其中的许多产品进行了测试，并选出了最适合大多数人的健身追踪器。</p><h2>健身追踪器最擅长什么？</h2><p>答案似乎很简单：健身追踪器最擅长监测锻炼情况，无论是绕街区步行 10 分钟，还是您一直在努力训练的半程马拉松。显然，智能手表也可以帮助您实现健身目标，但健身手环在某些方面已被证明是最佳选择：焦点、设计、电池寿命和价格。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当我说“专注”时，我指的是健身追踪器是为了很好地追踪活动而设计的。其他的都是额外的。它们通常没有智能手表所具有的附加功能，这可能会分散他们的健康追踪能力。它们的传感器和内部组件也较少，这使得它们更小、更轻。对于那些只想整天佩戴不那么显眼的设备的人来说，健身追踪器也是一个更好的选择。</p><p>健身追踪器的电池寿命也往往更长。虽然大多数智能手表一次充电可持续一到两天，但健身手环的电池续航时间可达五到七天，而且即使启用了睡眠跟踪功能，也可以全天和整夜使用。</p><p>就价格而言，没有竞争。大多数有价值的智能手表起价为 175 至 200 美元，但您可以购买一款起价为 70 美元的可靠健身追踪器。是的，存在更昂贵的腕带（我们在这里推荐一些），但您会在健身追踪器领域找到比智能手表领域更多 150 美元以下的选择。</p><h2>何时购买智能手表</h2><p>如果您对可穿戴设备的需求更多，那么智能手表可能是您的最佳选择。有些东西比如手表上的应用程序、提醒，甚至还有智能手表所具备的、而最好的健身追踪器所没有的更强大的健身功能。您可以使用它来控制智能家电、设置计时器和提醒、查看天气预报等。某些智能手表允许您选择要从哪些应用程序接收警报，并且选项不仅仅是通话和短信通知。</p><p>但在健身追踪器和智能手表之间做出选择时，额外的健身功能可以说是最重要的考虑因素。后者的设备往往更大，为 GPS、气压计、板载音乐存储等提供了更多空间。虽然您可以在某些健身追踪器上找到内置 GPS，但这并不常见。</p><h2>整体最佳：Fitbit Charge 5</h2><p><core-commerce id="574d2b23c43547ea983aeb4d4291cc0d" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAei71E0j4zfPdx287RPvt48GigKc7mOx2mThInYF_KAp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-Advanced-Management-Tracking-Graphite%2Fdp%2FB09BXQ4HMB%3F&amp;uuid=AyTHmoTHO9hud2S011912">Fitbit 的 Charge 5</a>拥有大多数人想要的健身追踪器的一切。首先，它不是智能手表。这意味着它在手腕上的轮廓略低，一次充电可持续数天，同时跟踪活动并监测您的心率、步数和睡眠。它还配备了全彩 AMOLED 显示屏，与之前的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Ftem4udG8vM0FFN0JjUj91dWlkPXUzem5XaU9abWJMQTRKMEYxMjkxMiIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNGFkMWJlNDAtMGEyOS0zZjMwLTg5YzMtYzhmMWE5MDM0Y2NmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAblC85yasyJxbdI4HObQXM3htBkzOU20-aIRQVHZbngg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F3AE7BcR%3Fuuid%3Du3znWiOZmbLA4J0F12912">Charge 4</a>上较小的灰度屏幕相比，这是一个很大的改进。该显示屏加上更薄的设计，使<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fitbit-charge-5-review-130043489.html">Charge 5</a>比其前身感觉更优质。</p><p> Charge 5 配备用于压力水平跟踪的 EDA 传感器，最终将支持心电图测量和每日准备度分数（后者仅适用于 Fitbit Premium 用户）。这些都是从 Charge 4 继承下来的现有功能之上的——最引人注目的是 Fitbit Pay 支持和内置 GPS 跟踪。前者可以让你通过滑动手腕来支付咖啡或杂货的费用，而后者则可以帮助绘制户外跑步、骑自行车和其他活动的地图。内置 GPS 仍然是本次展会的明星 - 它快速且准确，如果您想要一款专注的全能可穿戴健身手表，那么 Charge 5 是最佳选择。</p><h2>亚军：Garmin Vivosmart 5</h2><p><core-commerce id="03ea8ce28a29473381113742bfefc1ce" data-type="product-list"></p><p>价格更精致的健身手环替代品是售价<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbgrmhI1VbPPxgju0cNvk4jMwo7GYfSYxIOyxg8ezSKb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09VY5NRL5%2F&amp;uuid=irXplmCfd2jwpFsf16915">150 美元的 Garmin Vivosmart 5</a> 。它比 Fitbit Charge 5 更薄，更适合搭配手镯和您可能经常佩戴的其他珠宝。但其引人注目的设计只是其吸引力的一部分——Garmin 知道如何跟踪健身情况，Vivosmart 5 证明您无需花费数百美元购买该公司的一款深度健身手表即可获得一款功能强大的设备。</p><p>除了内置 GPS 之外，它具有许多与 Charge 5 相同的功能。不过，它确实支持联网 GPS，因此只要您随身携带手机，您就可以绘制户外跑步和骑自行车的地图。 Vivosmart 5 跟踪全天心律和活动，以及睡眠数据和锻炼，我们一直很欣赏 Garmin 可以选择的锻炼方案。您可以自定义在您的设备上显示的内容，并随时更改它们。您还可以获得额外的健康和保健信息，例如 Garmin 的身体电池分数（它会告诉您在剧烈锻炼后需要等待多长时间才能再次以最佳状态进行训练）、血氧水平、睡眠阶段数据、女性月经周期监控等。</p><p> Vivosmart 5 进行健身追踪的最大缺点是前面提到的缺乏内置​​ GPS，而且移动应用程序的使用稍显困难。但另一方面，Garmin 设备可以与 Apple Health 同步，而 Fitbit 设备仍然没有该功能。</p><h2>最佳预算：Fitbit Inspire 3</h2><p><core-commerce id="b4fc1105462f45dfbe7fbb5fdaf1298a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您只有 100 美元的闲钱， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcxkW_Rzze1B6EmaU4ZQsOz4p7a-dMD9RjtZhsLP7Dph&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B5F9SZW7%2F&amp;uuid=28j6QrwxKCXGHre820915">Fitbit Inspire 3</a>是最好的健身追踪器选择。它去掉了 Charge 5 的所有豪华功能，只保留了基本的跟踪功能。您不会获得内置 GPS 跟踪或 Fitbit Pay 或 Spotify 控制，但您可以获得出色的活动跟踪、自动锻炼检测、智能手机提醒等等。更新后的版本具有更时尚的设计，包括彩色触摸显示屏和连接的 GPS，后者可让您在携带手机在户外跑步或骑自行车时跟踪配速和距离。</p><p> Inspire 3 绝对是此列表中两款 Fitbit 设备中更时尚的一款。它的可互换表带让您可以随时切换智能设备的外观和感觉，而且它足够纤薄，可以与您可能佩戴的其他珠宝融为一体。它的多天电池续航时间也给我们留下了深刻的印象：Fitbit 承诺一次充电可达 10 天，这对我们来说是事实。经过四天的全天候使用，Inspire 3 的电量还剩 66%。</p><h2>最时尚：Withings Move</h2><p><core-commerce id="bb265a20e702442c8c26a04249494d69" data-type="product-list"></p><p>前面提到的所有健身追踪器都以自己的方式吸引人（对于那些具有可互换表带的人来说是加分项），但它们的外观相似。这些设备不再有很多替代设计。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9XaXRoaW5ncy1Nb3ZlLUFjdGl2aXR5LVRyYWNraW5nLVdhdGNoL2RwL0IwN0w2WlhYTks_cmVmXz1hc3Rfc3RvX2RwJnRoPTEmcHNjPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNDYtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRhZDFiZTQwLTBhMjktM2YzMC04OWMzLWM4ZjFhOTAzNGNjZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdbfr2PcJbQMDdHv1QwsuOkGmc7GiYs6oSnZevEEc_fV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWithings-Move-Activity-Tracking-Watch%2Fdp%2FB07L6ZXXNK%3Fref_%3Dast_sto_dp%26th%3D1%26psc%3D1&amp;uuid=rv5M2ADuJHSFyb5524916">售价 95 美元的 Withings Move 手表</a>是一个例外，它是您能买到的最传统时尚的健身追踪器之一。它是一款模拟表盘，具有多种健康监测功能，包括步数、卡路里、距离和睡眠跟踪、联网 GPS、自动识别 30 多种锻炼以及防水设计。但我们真的很喜欢它的超长电池寿命：在纽扣电池需要更换之前，它可以持续长达 18 个月。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-fitness-trackers-133053484.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-fitness-trackers-133053484.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4ad1be40-0a29-3f30-89c3-c8f1a9034ccf</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 16:50:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694019027</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T16:50:34+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[fitnesstrackers]]></category><category><![CDATA[Withings]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[wearables]]></category><category><![CDATA[Samsung]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[Fitbit]]></category><category><![CDATA[Garmin]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicEquipment,Instruments&Components]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicsAccessories]]></category><category><![CDATA[OfficeElectronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology&Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Health]]></category><category><![CDATA[Fitness]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Valentina Palladino]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-09/7aa28b90-1fb4-11ec-bbff-102b321bbc00" width="1800"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-09/7aa28b90-1fb4-11ec-bbff-102b321bbc00" width="1800"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Valentina Palladino / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Fitbit Charge 5 fitness tracker]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Fitbit Charge 5]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[YouTube is testing bitesize games on desktop and mobile]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> YouTube 正在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://support.google.com/youtube/thread/18138167/youtube-test-features-and-experiments">推出一个适用于小型游戏的应用内平台，</a>增加了您与流行视频服务上的内容互动的方式。遗憾的是，这并不是成熟的云游戏体验——可以把它想象成生活在社交视频网站中的 Miniclip。</p><p>这是一项实验性产品，因此仅适用于选定的参与者或 Beta 测试人员。如何知道自己是否被选中？打开 YouTube 并在主页内容旁边查找“可播放内容”选项卡。对于少数幸运者来说，游戏可以在桌面网站和移动设备上运行。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>目前还没有发布的游戏列表，但<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://9to5google.com/2023/09/05/youtube-testing-playables-gaming-effort/"><em><ins>9to5Google</ins></em><ins>报道</ins></a>称，有一款名为<em>Stack Bounce</em>的游戏，其中包括通过适时的点击将球击碎环。如果这个标题听起来很熟悉，那是因为 Google 的 GameSnacks 服务已经提供了<em>Stack Bounce</em> 。</p><p>此外，移动 3D 球与 Google Stadia 关闭时提供的游戏类型相去甚远，尽管该公司指出该系统将保存游戏进度，可通过“历史记录”选项卡访问。换句话说，更复杂的体验可能即将到来，因为当移动弹跳球穿过环时，没有太多进展可以保存。但就目前而言，它是迷你游戏的存储库。</p><p> YouTube 并不是唯一一家涉足云游戏的视频流服务商。过去几年，Netflix 大力进军该领域，最近<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-starts-testing-game-streaming-on-select-devices-smart-tvs-and-desktop-browsers-175241762.html"><ins>将服务扩展至部分智能电视</ins></a>和个人电脑。除了有现金奖励的现场问答比赛之外<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-has-reportedly-been-conducting-test-in-preparation-for-a-major-gaming-push-131551828.html"><ins>，甚至 TikTok 也在尝试简单的应用内游戏</ins></a>。谷歌的 Stadia 云流媒体服务早在一月份就陷入困境。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-testing-bitesize-games-on-desktop-and-mobile-163742756.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-testing-bitesize-games-on-desktop-and-mobile-163742756.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 087d9e12-356c-49ec-abbf-91cbcdb00fa4</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 16:37:42 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694018263</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T16:37:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="3950" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/ec9330e0-4ccd-11ee-8fef-ef58885bc85b" width="5925"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3950" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/ec9330e0-4ccd-11ee-8fef-ef58885bc85b" width="5925"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Unsplash/Christian Wiediger]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An image showing YouTube.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[YouTube ]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[EU confirms the six tech giants subject to its strict new competition laws]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欧盟已确认前六家科技“看门人” <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tech-giant-gatekeepers-must-comply-with-all-of-the-eus-new-digital-market-rules-065324264.html"><ins>需要遵守欧盟《数字市场法案》(DMA) 下严格的新规则</ins></a>。这些公司的名字大家应该都很熟悉：Alphabet、亚马逊、苹果、字节跳动、Meta 和微软。欧盟执行部门欧盟委员会（EC） <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_23_4328" data-original-link="https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_23_4328"><ins>指出</ins></a>，在评估某些公司是否达到了与收入、估值和用户数量相关的门槛后，三星尚未被指定为看门人。</p><p>欧盟委员会规定，“如果数字平台在企业和消费者之间提供与核心平台服务相关的重要网关”，则可以将其指定为看门人。守门人现在必须在 2024 年 3 月之前确保其适用的服务符合 DMA 法规。在这六家公司中，欧盟委员会指定了该法律适用的 22 项核心平台服务：</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><ul><li><p> Alphabet：Google 广告、Google 搜索、Android、YouTube、Chrome、Google 地图、Google Play 和 Google 购物</p></li><li><p>亚马逊：亚马逊商城和亚马逊广告</p></li><li><p>苹果：iOS、App Store 和 Safari</p></li><li><p>字节跳动：TikTok</p></li><li><p>元：Facebook、Instagram、WhatsApp、Messenger、元市场和元广告</p></li><li><p>微软：LinkedIn 和 Windows</p></li></ul><p> DMA <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://commission.europa.eu/strategy-and-policy/priorities-2019-2024/europe-fit-digital-age/digital-markets-act-ensuring-fair-and-open-digital-markets_en" data-original-link="https://commission.europa.eu/strategy-and-policy/priorities-2019-2024/europe-fit-digital-age/digital-markets-act-ensuring-fair-and-open-digital-markets_en"><ins>规定</ins></a>，看门人不能偏爱自己的服务而不是竞争对手的产品，也不能将用户锁定在自己的生态系统中。他们还必须让第三方实体在某些情况下与其服务进行互操作。</p><p>微软和苹果辩称，尽管 Bing、Edge、Microsoft Advertising 和 iMessage 达到了 EC 规定的门槛，但不符合网关资格，因此不必遵守 DMA。欧盟委员会已对每起案件展开市场调查，以审查各公司的主张。</p><p>与此同时，欧盟委员会指出，iPadOS 未达到门槛，但已展开市场调查，以确定是否应将其指定为核心平台服务。 Gmail、Outlook.com 和三星互联网浏览器确实达到了门槛，但它们各自的所有者（Alphabet、微软和三星）成功说服了 EC，这些服务都没有资格作为核心平台服务的网关。</p><p>这些规则可能会对苹果产生重大影响。尽管多年来越狱者一直在努力将应用程序侧载到 iPhone 上，但该公司仍试图在 iOS 生态系统周围保留防火墙。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-third-party-app-stores-report-195840839.html"><ins>此前有报道称</ins></a>，苹果将在 iOS 17 中<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://twitter.com/Kernel_9/status/1699394857750667756" data-original-link="https://twitter.com/Kernel_9/status/1699394857750667756"><ins>允许第三方应用商店</ins></a>和侧载——我们可以在下周该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-pro-set-to-feature-a-thinner-bezel-titanium-frame-and-usb-c-charging-094118389.html"><ins>举行秋季 iPhone 活动</ins></a>时了解更多相关信息。微软（ <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-head-says-microsofts-mobile-game-store-could-arrive-next-year-180007168.html"><ins>特别是 Xbox</ins></a> ）和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/epic-loses-bid-to-make-apple-change-its-app-store-payment-rules-right-now-174924222.html"><ins>Epic Games 等</ins></a>公司正在准备自己的移动应用商店，以应对 iOS 花园崩溃的情况。</p><p>到目前为止，苹果还拒绝了谷歌（ <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/drake-texts-go-green-apple-google-rcs-161802322.html"><ins>有点尴尬</ins></a>）说服它支持 RCS 消息传递标准的努力。前者非常<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tim-cook-response-green-bubbles-android-your-mom-095538175.html"><ins>了解iMessage和蓝色文本气泡的价值</ins></a>。然而，如果欧盟委员会指定 iMessage 作为网关，苹果可能会被迫与 RCS 和其他消息服务好好合作。</p><p>为此，苹果告诉<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:11;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-says-it-remains-worried-about-risks-eu-digital-markets-act-2023-09-06/?utm_source=pocket_saves" data-original-link="https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-says-it-remains-worried-about-risks-eu-digital-markets-act-2023-09-06/?utm_source=pocket_saves"><em><ins>路透社</ins></em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>其担心 DMA 合规性可能会出现隐私和安全风险。该公司表示：“我们的重点将是如何减轻这些影响，并继续为欧洲客户提供最好的产品和服务。”</p><p>如果网守不遵守 DMA 规则，可能会产生严重后果。欧盟委员会可对侵权守门人处以高达其全球营业额 10% 的罚款。如果看门人继续违反规则，这一比例可能会上升到 20%。 EC 还赋予自己权力，在系统性 DMA 违规的情况下，强制看门人出售业务并阻止其购买相关服务。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/eu-confirms-the-six-tech-giants-subject-to-its-strict-new-competition-laws-161917822.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/eu-confirms-the-six-tech-giants-subject-to-its-strict-new-competition-laws-161917822.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 159b09cc-1f0e-4a42-8d2e-1d4988ecf3b7</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 16:19:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694017159</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T16:19:26+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1125" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2018-12/d0163680-021b-11e9-bf9f-201f0e6696ec" width="1500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1125" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-images/2018-12/d0163680-021b-11e9-bf9f-201f0e6696ec" width="1500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[European Union flag waving outside European Commission headquarters, Brussels, Belgium, photo]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[European Union flag waving outside European Commission headquarters, Brussels, Belgium, photo]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best Bluetooth trackers for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您曾因丢失钥匙或钱包而无法准时出发，那么蓝牙追踪器将为您带来帮助。这些小工具连接到您的物品上，并使用您的智能手机来监视它们的位置。现在此类小工具的数量越来越多，我们测试了一些最受欢迎的选项，以找到我们的首选，并帮助您决定哪一个是最适合您的蓝牙跟踪器。</p><h2>在蓝牙跟踪设备中寻找什么</h2><p>蓝牙跟踪器是小光盘或卡，依靠短距离、低能量的无线信号与智能手机进行通信。将一个芯片贴在您的物品上，如果它在范围内，您的手机可以“响铃”该芯片，以便您找到它。这些跟踪设备还提供其他功能，例如分离警报，告诉您何时遗留了标记的物品，或者上次检测到丢失物品的位置。当您超出范围时，有些甚至可以利用更大的智能手机网络来追踪您的设备。根据您希望跟踪器执行的操作，在决定购买哪个时需要考虑一些规格。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h3><strong>设备兼容性</strong></h3><p>与库比蒂诺的人们提供的大多数产品一样， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airtags-trackers-first-look-hands-on-130036848.html">AirTags</a>只适用于 Apple 生态系统中的产品。不过，该公司已向包括 Chipolo 在内的第三方制造商开放其 Find My 网络的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLXVzL0hUMjExMzMxIzp-OnRleHQ9U3VwcG9ydGVkJTIwdGhpcmQlMkRwYXJ0eSUyMHByb2R1Y3RzJnRleHQ9VGhlJTIwZm9sbG93aW5nJTIwcHJvZHVjdHMlMjBhcmUlMjBjb21wYXRpYmxlLHdpdGglMjB0aGUlMjBTREQlMjBGaW5kaW5nJTIwc3lzdGVtIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI2M2IxMjRmOC0yNjVkLTQ5YTctOWQxMS01MmU2NzFiZWMwYzYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcs6otxYTaPJkVFkCTdYh98uCdvHslF2hmlbiiNv9pbj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT211331%23%3A%7E%3Atext%3DSupported%2520third%252Dparty%2520products%26text%3DThe%2520following%2520products%2520are%2520compatible%2Cwith%2520the%2520SDD%2520Finding%2520system&amp;uuid=fDQCO0BMVEVlXsrB8153">访问权限</a>。其 One Spot 和 Card Spot 探测器可与 Apple 的大型追踪网络配合使用，但仅与 Apple 设备配对。 Chipolo 的经典追踪器可与 Android 或 Apple 设备配合使用，Tile 追踪器也是如此。</p><h3><strong>寻找网络</strong></h3><p>众包寻找能力成为头条新闻，其中包括追回被盗<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://9to5mac.com/2022/05/09/airtag-stolen-gear/">设备</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.newsweek.com/couple-tracking-lost-luggage-journey-apple-airtag-wow-viewers-1733614">在全球范围内</a>追踪丢失行李的故事。这些蓝牙跟踪设备使用匿名信号对其他人的设备进行 ping 操作，即使您的智能手机不在蓝牙范围内，也可能会告诉您标记的物品在哪里。 Apple 的“查找我的”网络是迄今为止最大的，超过 10 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-count-over-1-billion-045552737.html">亿</a>台正在使用的 iPhone 默认都运行 Apple 的“查找我的”应用程序。因此，除非 iPhone 用户选择退出，否则他们的手机会默默地充当任何附近 AirTags 的位置检测器。</p><p>尽管 Android 手机在全球范围内的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/android-dominates-globally-but-apples-gaining-ground-102346830.html">数量超过了</a>iPhone，但它们还没有类似的统一网络。在今年的 I/O 大会上，谷歌<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-io-2023-everything-announced-at-the-event-193758196.html">宣布</a>即将对其“查找我的设备”网络进行升级，首先是更好的反跟踪措施，其中一些措施是<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-rolls-out-anti-stalking-measures-for-airtag-and-other-bluetooth-trackers-194936293.html">最近推出的</a>。 FindMy 竞争对手网络的全面推出已推迟到今年年底。我们知道一些跟踪器将利用新系统，一旦它们可用，我们将对其进行测试并更新本指南。</p><p>与此同时，Tile 提供了第二大的查找网格，每部运行 Tile 应用程序的智能手机都充当隐身定位器。 Life360 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Life360;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=7d4ad158-ef3c-4076-800c-a48ae1e8937e&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Life360&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI3ZDRhZDE1OC1lZjNjLTQwNzYtODAwYy1hNDhhZTFlODkzN2UiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubGlmZTM2MC5jb20vYmxvZy90aWxlLWpvaW5zLWxpZmUzNjAvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI2M2IxMjRmOC0yNjVkLTQ5YTctOWQxMS01MmU2NzFiZWMwYzYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAUTqZnrTq_j9lZCvmXv0wW7fTw_pRZ9WHKm3VdGluDyk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.life360.com%2Fblog%2Ftile-joins-life360%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.life360.com/blog/tile-joins-life360/">收购</a>Tile 后，该应用程序的 4700 万用户添加到现有的 5000 万 Tile 用户中，形成了一个相当大的网络。</p><p>在我们的测试中，AirTags 提供了近乎实时的位置数据，并且能够以最快的速度找到阿尔伯克基周边地区被遗弃的物品，包括诺布山 (Nob Hill) 的酒吧、书店和咖啡店，以及新墨西哥大学校园内的各种户外场所。蓝牙跟踪块大多数时候都能够定位我们丢失的物品，尽管其精确度不如 AirTags。 Chipolo 的 Spot 追踪器在同一个“查找我的”网络上运行，并且性能与 AirTags 相当。</p><p>另一方面，Chipolo 的经典追踪器并没有太多的众包网络可言。然而，当我们使用跟踪器时，面对典型的日常用例，发现网络的大小开始变得不那么重要。正是他们在各个方面都表现出色的能力，使 Chipolo 的经典追踪器跻身我们榜单的榜首。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/94489620-abc7-11ed-b375-842957054bf1" alt="各种蓝牙追踪器排列在木质背景上的网格中。追踪器包括各种形状的黑色 Tile 追踪器、两个银色和白色的 AirTag 追踪器以及一个通过多功能工具钥匙链连接到一组钥匙的圆形蓝色 Chipolo 追踪器。" data-uuid="e92fd876-b075-3bd1-9c92-355d3b241508"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">艾米·斯科海姆 / Engadget</div></figure><h3><strong>分离警报</strong></h3><p>这就是追踪器日常实用性真正发挥作用的地方。当您离开标记的物品太远时，分离警报会通知您，如果您想确保您的笔记本电脑包、夹克或雨伞在您离开家时始终随身携带，这非常有用。</p><p>当您外出时，这些通知也会起作用。如果您的钱包里有蓝牙跟踪设备，但走出餐厅时却没有带它，那么分离警报就会启动，从而减少丢失的物品。此功能还可以告诉您标记的物品和手机上次配对的位置，以便您在错过警报时可以追溯您的步骤。</p><p>每个跟踪器处理遗留物品的方式都不同。 AirTags 和 Chipolo 默认都包含该功能。 Tile 跟踪器需要每年<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=9a27b27f-6486-47c7-9cdc-0c4040bd9690&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Tile&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI5YTI3YjI3Zi02NDg2LTQ3YzctOWNkYy0wYzQwNDBiZDk2OTAiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGlsZS5jb20vZW4tdXMvcGxhbnMiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYzYjEyNGY4LTI2NWQtNDlhNy05ZDExLTUyZTY3MWJlYzBjNiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAS3gS-ptxLvKi9M17Nfp7mkMV8Ej-2v8XP5fJ2qSd8Fr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tile.com%2Fen-us%2Fplans&amp;uuid=Jg5abHgGg2GW29IW10154">订阅</a>才能启用警报（目前每年 30 美元）。 AirTags 和 Tiles 都允许您关闭某些位置的分离警报，这意味着您可以将家设置为可以留下物品的“安全”地方，但警报仍会在其他地方触发。 Chipolo 不提供安全位置，但您可以针对每个项目切换超出范围警报。</p><p>在我们的测试中，当我们距离标记的物品 250 到 450 英尺时，Chipolo 会发出警报。 AirTags 在 600 英尺到 1,400 英尺之间向我们发出警报。 Tiles 在平均约 1,500 英尺后发送了通知。磁贴通知在 iPhone 上并不一致，但在 Android 手机上运行良好。</p><h3><strong>连接性、体积和设计</strong></h3><p>您可能最常使用的功能是简单的“查找我的钥匙”功能。如果您有手机，但不知道标记的钥匙在哪里，则可以点击跟踪器应用程序中的按钮以使跟踪器响铃。 Tile 和 Chipolo 经典追踪器还允许您双击设备本身以使手机响铃，但在“查找我的”应用程序上运行的 AirTags 和 Chipolos 不提供此功能。</p><p>蓝牙跟踪设备的音量可能决定您是否可以找到埋在沙发垫中或嘈杂房间中的物品。 AirTags 因安静而闻名，这与我们所看到的相符（测量值约为 65 分贝）。 Chipolo 的钥匙扣式标签（仅限 Apple 版本和与设备无关的版本）以及 Tile Slim 钱包追踪器的声音最大，测量值在 83 至 85 分贝之间。</p><p>设计将决定您可以将追踪器连接到什么地方。 AirTags 是小而光滑的圆盘，如果没有配件，就无法固定到任何东西上，配件<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-apple-airtag-cases-holders-accessories-123036404.html">数量众多</a>，但这是需要考虑的额外成本。 Chipolo 和 Tile 都提供带有孔的追踪器，可以轻松连接到您的钥匙圈上，两家公司还提供卡片形状的版本，旨在适合您的钱包。 AirTags、Chipolo One 和 Tile Pro 的电池可更换。 Tile Mate 和所有卡片状追踪器都没有可更换电池，这意味着当整个设备没电时，您必须更换整个设备。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3BlYmJsZWJlZS5jb20vIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI2M2IxMjRmOC0yNjVkLTQ5YTctOWQxMS01MmU2NzFiZWMwYzYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYa8jjhHxuQK8FJhfeAcbhRErxJiGnQTNySgp26XM-Ya&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fpebblebee.com%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://pebblebee.com/">Pebblebee</a>追踪器是可充电的。我们目前正在测试它们，并将更新本指南以分享它们的叠加方式。</p><h3><strong>跟踪和偷窃</strong></h3><p>AirTags 最近引起了很多关注，因为不良行为者将其<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airtag-stalking-police-reports-190022315.html">植入</a>人们身上以跟踪他们。虽然这一事实可能不会影响您的购买决定，但任何有关蓝牙跟踪器的讨论都应注意<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLXVzL0hUMjEyMjI3IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI2M2IxMjRmOC0yNjVkLTQ5YTctOWQxMS01MmU2NzFiZWMwYzYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAe9wp3dHWI77shmqqj-OBkY-SU2Wc70hbQ2fXQmBCFSp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT212227" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT212227">苹果</a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-rolls-out-anti-stalking-measures-for-airtag-and-other-bluetooth-trackers-194936293.html">谷歌</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tile-tag-scan-and-secure-anti-stalking-175822554.html">Tile</a>已采取哪些措施来解决该问题。如果检测到 AirTag <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-convinced-my-dog-is-stalking-me-143100932.html">与您一起移动</a>且远离其所有者，设备将发出铃声以<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-update-hidden-airtags-easier-to-locate-092003140.html">提醒您</a>它的存在。无论您使用的是 iPhone 还是 Android 手机，只要您打开了定位服务和蓝牙，您就会自动收到警报，无需采取进一步的步骤。 Tile 通过其标准应用程序提供了类似的功能，并且不需要 Tile 帐户即可搜索附近可疑的跟踪器。</p><p>最近，Tile 推出了一项名为防盗模式的功能，该功能使您能够使其跟踪器之一不被其他人检测到。这意味着如果有人偷了您的标记物品，他们将无法使用反跟踪功能来找到其精确位置并禁用跟踪器。当然，这可能会使 Tile 更容易用作跟踪设备，因此为了启用该功能，您必须验证您的 ID 并同意因滥用而被处以<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tile-thinks-a-1-million-fine-will-deter-stalkers-from-using-its-trackers-181857358.html">100 万美元的罚款</a>。</p><p>一般来说，蓝牙跟踪器可能是也可能不是打击盗窃的最佳选择。人们使用追踪器找回被盗物品的轶事比比皆是，但其他故事则更具<a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.cbsnews.com/newyork/news/exclusive-man-tracks-his-stolen-motorcycle-in-brooklyn-then-gets-in-fight-with-suspected-thieves/?uuid=msvElrzASiWkkNSa23031">警示意义</a>。苹果仍然没有推广其追踪器或寻找网络作为应对盗窃的方法。另一方面，GPS 跟踪器通常就是为了这个目的而销售的。</p><h2>我们如何测试</h2><p>在决定测试哪些追踪器之前，我们对该领域进行了研究，查看了亚马逊、百思买和其他零售商的用户评论，以及 Reddit 等网站上的讨论。在将我们的选择范围缩小到 Apple AirTag、Tile 和 Chipolo 追踪器之前，我们还查看了其他出版物对此事的看法。</p><p>以下是我们测试的每个跟踪器的完整列表：</p><ul><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDkzM0JWSzZULz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby1sYS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNjNiMTI0ZjgtMjY1ZC00OWE3LTlkMTEtNTJlNjcxYmVjMGM2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAQlp7JRCkzhujBL4AclgW7F8yJUv2nZZTbBMqKnF9uBR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F">苹果航空标签</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9UaWxlLUJsdWV0b290aC1CYXR0ZXJ5LVdhdGVyLVJlc2lzdGFudC1Db21wYXRpYmxlL2RwL0IwOTk5OE1CRk0_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbGEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYzYjEyNGY4LTI2NWQtNDlhNy05ZDExLTUyZTY3MWJlYzBjNiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcJ-hqhAd_uoCK-efNMqwufuaKQGFQkG-kUAtiFetrxw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTile-Bluetooth-Battery-Water-Resistant-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB09998MBFM">瓷砖伴侣</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdXOdxTBtCAHitdmq1AiKoc-LvadwEGqV7YICfAZdRqN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTile-Powerful-Bluetooth-Water-Resistant-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB09B2WLRWX">瓷砖专业版</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX3Nom_KP_hYwX1AS5BU_ZI5CO7F4TF2k3EiqENgBpfZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTile-1-Pack-Bluetooth-Water-Resistant-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB09B2NYJ3T">瓷砖超薄</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2NoaXBvbG8ubmV0L2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL2NoaXBvbG8tY2FyZC1zcG90P2NsPWhlYWRlciIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNjNiMTI0ZjgtMjY1ZC00OWE3LTlkMTEtNTJlNjcxYmVjMGM2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAQAtATonSXh9ZUR6Nk07BvZJMiEj_eP73L04Hq2bnXyh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fchipolo.net%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fchipolo-card-spot%3Fcl%3Dheader">Chipolo 卡现货</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeFl8KreCE_w4Lj5S59_oP7B-RPSj1oVEOUvrPy8g3FF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-Card-Spot-Bluetooth-Tracker%2Fdp%2FB09ZTZ47K4%3Fref_%3Dast_sto_dp%26th%3D1%26psc%3D1">奇波洛一处</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXaM4TT3CVg8yhY8pi_F3NLzIp7Xm13WreEHB94PoILh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-ONE-Loudest-Resistant-Bluetooth%2Fdp%2FB0832YCWHV" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Chipolo-ONE-Loudest-Resistant-Bluetooth/dp/B0832YCWHV">奇波罗一号</a></p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9DaGlwb2xvLUNhcmQtUmVzaXN0YW50LUJsdWV0b290aC1UcmFja2VyL2RwL0IwODRLWTFKMTU_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbGEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYzYjEyNGY4LTI2NWQtNDlhNy05ZDExLTUyZTY3MWJlYzBjNiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAATK3aBCavwAQUutLH-nih8tS3hD9bW3LHcC3XZxZDht5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-Card-Resistant-Bluetooth-Tracker%2Fdp%2FB084KY1J15">奇波罗卡</a></p></li></ul><p>购买追踪器后，我使用 iPhone 11 和三星 Galaxy S22 Ultra 在几周的时间里对每个追踪器进行了测试。我重新创造了可能的用户体验，例如在家里和城外丢失和遗留物品。我在阿尔伯克基市中心附近的不同地点种植了追踪器，主要集中在新墨西哥大学及其周边地区以及诺布山周边地区。每个测试都会在步行和驾驶时进行多次，我使用谷歌地图上的测量距离功能来跟踪警报的镜头。我关注了该应用程序的易用性、手机与追踪器连接的可靠性以及常规使用过程中出现的任何其他优点和缺点。</p><h2>最佳整体奖：Chipolo One </h2><p><core-commerce id="b8337d2138ba406ab634cd46926816c9" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>动手测试非常适合打破假设， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXaM4TT3CVg8yhY8pi_F3NLzIp7Xm13WreEHB94PoILh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-ONE-Loudest-Resistant-Bluetooth%2Fdp%2FB0832YCWHV" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Chipolo-ONE-Loudest-Resistant-Bluetooth/dp/B0832YCWHV">Chipolo One</a>就是这样。该追踪器的众包查找网络无法与苹果的 AirTag 或 Tile 相比。事实上，当我离开新墨西哥大学繁忙的学生会外面的 Chipolo 24 小时时，我从未收到过 Chipolo <a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2NoaXBvbG8ubmV0L2VuLXVzL3BhZ2VzL2NvbW11bml0eSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNjNiMTI0ZjgtMjY1ZC00OWE3LTlkMTEtNTJlNjcxYmVjMGM2In0&amp;signature=AQAAATI2APUmcRWwTBLUMtXwsVojoxx3nxv3q3QP9ocvldHZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fchipolo.net%2Fen-us%2Fpages%2Fcommunity&amp;uuid=Tu5i2PguJiSroJue24173">社区</a>成员发现了我的物品的提醒。但当我使用它并想象大多数人每天如何使用追踪器时，该设备证明了它的价值，并在我的钥匙圈上赢得了一席之地。</p><p> One 是一个带有孔的彩色小塑料圆盘。它适用于 Apple 和 Android 设备，并且需要一个易于使用且易于配对新跟踪器的应用程序。 iPhone 和 Galaxy 手机上的应用程序和跟踪体验几乎相同，在两个平台上运行得同样好。 It rang the loudest of all the trackers, so lost items were quickly found around the house. Unlike other trackers, there was never a delay between pressing the Ring to Find button and hearing the trill. The ring delay for AirTag was never more than a few seconds and Tiles would generally connect and ring after no more than ten seconds. While that&#39;s not a deal-breaking delay, it could add to the stress of rushing out the door.</p><p> Where the Chipolo One truly set itself apart was with its separation alerts. I would only get a half to two blocks away (or an average of 350 feet) before getting an alert asking if I&#39;d forgotten an item. Neither AirTag nor Tile ever beat Chipolo to the punch. The alerts were consistent whether I was forgetting an item at home, at a coffee shop, or inside my car.</p><p> As far as losing stuff out in the wild, it will get you back to the spot where your phone and tracker were last paired. That means if you miss an alert or don&#39;t have them turned on, Chipolo will give you directions (via your maps app) and take you right to where you left your item. In one test, I had a friend hide the tracker nearby when I wasn&#39;t looking. I left the area and returned hours later, using the last location information to lead me within a few feet of the tracker&#39;s precise location. Ringing the tracker then made it easy to find. Of course, if someone walks off with your tracked item, the Chipolo will be harder pressed to help you out.</p><p> If you&#39;re concerned about lost <a data-i13n="cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/faa-apple-airtags-allowed-in-checked-baggage-181915494.html">luggage</a> when you travel or if you worry you may lose things on trains or buses, this isn&#39;t the tracker for you because of its much smaller finding network. But if you&#39;re looking for a dead simple way to find your keys and make sure your jacket leaves the bar when you do, the Chipolo One is hard to beat.</p><h2> Best for iPhones: AirTag </h2><p><core-commerce id="a197f7330c014bbeb53fe90bee419295" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAc5ZzLNwjJG6mIN9XaVHPNjo0oFXgfIKSOkLROnt2XGg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F&amp;uuid=4lk4kIolrELtraHg28175">AirTags</a> work with iOS&#39; Find My app, so they don&#39;t require any additional downloads. If you&#39;ve used the <a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/how-to-share-location-iphone-143002231.html">Find My app</a> before, you&#39;ll likely understand how this works. These are the quietest of the trackers we tested and each time you press the Play Sound button, the tags only ring for seven seconds. You&#39;ll need to keep pressing if you don&#39;t find your item right away and AirTags can&#39;t be used to ring your phone.</p><p> As for separation alerts, AirTags were consistent, always delivering a “left behind” alert when I traveled about 1,200 feet away, or about three square blocks, without an item. You can turn off separation alerts for any given tracker, as well as designate certain locations, such as your home or workplace, as exceptions for the notifications.</p><p> One feature that AirTags have that no other tag offers is the ability to tap into the ultra-wideband (UWB) wireless protocol. This allows you to play a fun game of hot and cold with an item when it&#39;s within about 25 feet of your iPhone. Directional arrows and a diminishing distance meter on your iPhone&#39;s screen point you to an item without having to ring it. This worked reliably about 75 percent of the time in my tests; sometimes it was just easier to ring the item when the directional finding couldn&#39;t keep a lock on the tracker.</p><p> UWB is supported by iPhone models 11 and later and while newer Galaxy and Pixel phones also support UWB, no Android-compatible tracker has yet been released. In 2021, Tile <a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tile-pro-ultra-wideband-tracker-new-devices-100025451.html">announced</a> one that would, but has since missed its promised release window of “early 2022.”</p><p> AirTag&#39;s ability to locate a lost item out in the city is almost eerie. I had someone (who was not carrying an iPhone) take my bike with a tracker hidden under the seat to a location a little over a half mile away. I set out a few minutes later and toggled on Notify When Found in the Find My app. Within three minutes, I received a notification that the bike had been “seen” near an address. Tapping on Directions navigates to Apple Maps, which took me to a spot about 30 feet from the bike. Had it been obscured from view, I could have then used the Find Nearby button to activate the UWB locating features. Ringing the tag was too quiet to hear on the sidewalk.</p><p> If you want the same scary-precise community finding features, but with a louder ring and a hole in the tracker, the <a data-i13n="cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeFl8KreCE_w4Lj5S59_oP7B-RPSj1oVEOUvrPy8g3FF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-Card-Spot-Bluetooth-Tracker%2Fdp%2FB09ZTZ47K4%3Fref_%3Dast_sto_dp%26th%3D1%26psc%3D1&amp;uuid=hjdRjnNYxcmrOvp929176">Chipolo One Spot</a> is a solid option. It doesn&#39;t offer UWB capabilities, however, and the separation alerts are the same as with AirTags (letting you get 1,200 feet away before a ping, versus an average of 350 feet with our top rec, Chipolo One classic).</p><h2> Best for Android: Tile Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="ae9d21da0a6647c595f16b9398e82c3b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Tile will work with either Android or Apple devices, but the experience is much better on Android. Certain connectivity issues and a lack of alerts that plagued the iPhone experience did not show up in tests with the Galaxy phone. One caveat to note is that Tile requires a subscription to enable separation alerts. Tile Premium goes for $3 per month or $30 per year and includes location history and item reimbursement of up to $100 on items that you register with the company, they&#39;ll also send out a fresh battery once a year. Tile stands out as the only tracker company offering reimbursement — even without a subscription, they&#39;ll pay out <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://tileteam.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360051207613-Tile-Basic-Reimbursement">up to $25</a> for items that you register with them.</p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdXOdxTBtCAHitdmq1AiKoc-LvadwEGqV7YICfAZdRqN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTile-Powerful-Bluetooth-Water-Resistant-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB09B2WLRWX&amp;uuid=5vr4VqSpWIAMS3ju32179">Tile Pro</a> is a key-fob shaped device with a metal keychain hole that feels sturdy. The Pro&#39;s ring was just a few decibels quieter than the Tile Mate (78 versus 82 decibels), but the connectivity range was better with the Pro, and it was more accurate in finder network tests. On top of that, this is the only current Tile device with a replaceable battery, which lasts about one year.</p><p> For the lost-item tests, I had a friend take the Pro to random locations. After turning on the Notify When Found feature, an alert would arrive between five and ten minutes later saying my lost item was “found by the community.” The map details were typically accurate within about 100 feet or so, though it occasionally thought the Tile was at a business next door to where it actually was. Without the UWB feature, precision finding of an item was trickier. In one test, the tracker ended up in a noisy pub. While the directions pointed me to the right location, it would have been difficult to find the item if I hadn&#39;t spotted my friend, as the ring function was useless among the din.</p><h2> Best wallet tracker: Tile Slim </h2><p><core-commerce id="18b914cc2e30469c9d772f949235721f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX3Nom_KP_hYwX1AS5BU_ZI5CO7F4TF2k3EiqENgBpfZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTile-1-Pack-Bluetooth-Water-Resistant-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB09B2NYJ3T&amp;uuid=8WzIVx2N4Tb90fyI35181">Tile Slim</a> is louder than both the Pro and the Mate, and nearly equals the loudest tracker we tested, the Chipolo One. It works with both Android and Apple devices and its thick credit card shape fits in the slots of a typical wallet (though it often won&#39;t connect when inside an RFID-blocking wallet). The separation alerts you&#39;ll get if you pay for a Tile subscription activate at about the same distance as the Tile Pro, letting you get around 1,500 feet away before pinging you about a left-behind item. When using an iPhone with Tile trackers, separation alerts rarely came and connectivity between the phone and tracker was spotty at best, even in close proximity. If you use an iPhone, the <a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2NoaXBvbG8ubmV0L2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL2NoaXBvbG8tY2FyZC1zcG90IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI2M2IxMjRmOC0yNjVkLTQ5YTctOWQxMS01MmU2NzFiZWMwYzYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXTP4qAUuuFl8Q2lvX7So4gum56gwplZGcYwoVF9zlzi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fchipolo.net%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fchipolo-card-spot&amp;uuid=e8tEyU79NPnHnQ7l36190">Chipolo Card Spot</a> is equally loud, runs on Apple&#39;s vast Find My network and consistently gives you a left-behind alert at around 1,200 feet.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-bluetooth-tracker-140028377.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-bluetooth-tracker-140028377.html?src=rss]]><source_id>engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 63b124f8-265d-49a7-9d11-52e671bec0c6</guid><dc:creator> Amy Skorheim</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 15:30:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694014209</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T15:30:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Amy Skorheim]]></category><media:content height="900" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/e688a350-4cb5-11ee-b8be-c476b99bbacb" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="900" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/e688a350-4cb5-